    <entry>
      <title>markdown note</title>
      <link href="/2021/07/20/markdown-note/"/>
      <url>/2021/07/20/markdown-note/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="格式"><a href="#格式" class="headerlink" title="格式"></a>格式</h2><h3 id="分割线"><a href="#分割线" class="headerlink" title="分割线"></a>分割线</h3><blockquote><p>我们可以通过输入三个或更多的「减号 -」、「星号 <em>」、「下划线 -」的方式创建一条相当于 HTML 语法中 <code>&lt;hr/&gt;</code> 一样的分隔线。这三个符号之间可以包含空格，每种类型的分隔线，可以表现为如下形式： * * <em>, **</em>, ****</em>, - - -, ———。</p></blockquote><h2 id="公式"><a href="#公式" class="headerlink" title="公式"></a>公式</h2><p>积分和花体<br>$$p(s_F|x)=\int_{\tau\in \mathcal{T}(c_p)}p(\tau|x)p(s_F|\tau,x)d\tau$$</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$$p(s<span class="emphasis">_F|x)=\int_</span>&#123;\tau\in \mathcal&#123;T&#125;(c<span class="emphasis">_p)&#125;p(\tau|x)p(s_</span>F|\tau,x)d\tau$$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      <categories>
          
          <category> markdown </category>
          
      </categories>
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>Hexo添加新的文章和添加新的标签页</title>
      <link href="/2021/07/19/my-new-pos/"/>
      <url>/2021/07/19/my-new-pos/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="添加"><a href="#添加" class="headerlink" title="添加"></a>添加</h2><h3 id="添加新的文章"><a href="#添加新的文章" class="headerlink" title="添加新的文章"></a>添加新的文章</h3><p>在source/_post中新建md类型的文档，也可以命令行创建</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo new &quot;post name&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>然后执行<code>hexo g</code>的时候会被渲染，开头需要一些yml信息\</p><p>再执行<code>hexo d</code>就可以将其部署到github上。</p><h3 id="添加”分类”页面"><a href="#添加”分类”页面" class="headerlink" title="添加”分类”页面"></a>添加”分类”页面</h3><p>新建一个分类页面</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo new page categories</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>修改source/categories/index.md</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: 分类</span><br><span class="line">date: 2021-07-19 22:54:58</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">--&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: 分类</span><br><span class="line">date: 2021-07-19 22:54:58</span><br><span class="line">type: &quot;categories&quot; (添加这行 空格需要注意)</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>themes\cactus下的_config.yml中的nav进行匹配</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">nav:</span><br><span class="line">  home: /</span><br><span class="line">  about: /about/</span><br><span class="line">  articles: /archives/</span><br><span class="line">  projects: projects_url</span><br><span class="line">  categories: /categories（添加此行即可）        </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>给文章添加categories属性</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: Hexo添加新的文章和添加新的标签页</span><br><span class="line">date: 2021-07-19 10:30:24</span><br><span class="line">categories: Exercise</span><br><span class="line">tags: first try</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>一开始添加后，发现标签名是英文<br>后来发现是themes/cactus/languages/zh-CN.yml没做好映射</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">nav:</span><br><span class="line">  home: 首页</span><br><span class="line">  about: 关于</span><br><span class="line">  articles: 归档</span><br><span class="line">  projects: 项目</span><br><span class="line">  tag: 标签</span><br><span class="line">  category: 分类</span><br><span class="line">  search: 搜索</span><br><span class="line">  categories: 分类（添加）</span><br><span class="line">  tags: 标签 (添加)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>当然开始时添加标签页改为，无复数形式也是可以的</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo new page category</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="添加”标签”页面"><a href="#添加”标签”页面" class="headerlink" title="添加”标签”页面"></a>添加”标签”页面</h3><p>与添加分类页面几乎完全相同</p><h3 id="添加”搜索”页面"><a href="#添加”搜索”页面" class="headerlink" title="添加”搜索”页面"></a>添加”搜索”页面</h3><p>需要npm安装hexo-generator-search，之后与添加分类页面几乎完全相同</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> npm install hexo-generator-search --save</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> hexo new page search</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在source/search/index.md添加</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">title: Search</span><br><span class="line">type: search</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>编辑theme/cactus/_config.yml</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">nav:</span><br><span class="line">  search: /search</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这里遇到一个问题，虽然不影响页面显示，但是error令人很不愉快</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ERROR &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  err: [Error: EISDIR: illegal operation on a directory, read] &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    errno: -4068,</span><br><span class="line">    code: &#x27;EISDIR&#x27;,</span><br><span class="line">    syscall: &#x27;read&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125; Plugin load failed: %s hexo-deployer-git</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>最后在网上搜索资料，利用一下命令解决</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-deployer-git -save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="参考链接"><a href="#参考链接" class="headerlink" title="参考链接"></a>参考链接</h3><p><a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/ebbbc8edcc24">Git个人博客hexo设置关于、标签、分类、归档、时间线</a><br><a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/e17711e44e00">Hexo使用攻略-添加分类及标签</a><br><a href="https://xiangyuwei.github.io/2017/12/04/Hexo%20+%20github%20%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E8%BF%87%E7%A8%8B/">Hexo + github 博客搭建过程</a><br><a href="https://github.com/probberechts/hexo-theme-cactus">cactus git 主页</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
      <categories>
          
          <category> Exercise </category>
          
      </categories>
      
      
